item.title: Injustice Gods Among Us Year 2 Vol 1
item.description: A New York Times Bestseller! The best-selling prequel to the hit video game picks up right where it left off! Year one is over - now, year two begins. The death of one of their own has divided Earth's protectors as hero turns against hero. As Superman's iron grip on the world tightens, at the edge of the galaxy, anothe grave threat approaches... Collects Injustice: Gods Among Us Year 2 #1-5.
